# 💥 5. Why threads? (Book reasons)

---

## 🟢 1. Concurrency

👉 network servers:

```text
multiple requests handle
```

---

## 🔵 2. Easier data sharing

👉 threads:

```text
same memory → easy sharing
```

👉 processes:

```text
separate memory → hard
```

---

## 🟡 3. Efficiency

👉 thread:

```text
lightweight
```

👉 process:

```text
heavy (context switch costly)
```

---

## 🔴 4. Parallelism (multi-core)

👉 multiple CPU இருந்தா:

```text
threads → true parallel execution
```

