# ⚙️ 6. Threads vs Processes (Deep clarity)

| Feature       | Process   | Thread  |
| ------------- | --------- | ------- |
| Memory        | separate  | shared  |
| Creation cost | high      | low     |
| Switching     | expensive | cheaper |
| Data sharing  | hard      | easy    |

